Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:08.92,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}生命在诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:13.80,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便此刻不知不觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:21.00,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心中却已接受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位住宿生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假最后的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宿舍主办的烧烤派对之夜现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此就这么几个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都还没从老家回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假还留在宿舍的人才不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的南方小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假不在这里度过不是太可惜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来本田学长在宿舍里面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙打工时受到的心灵创伤还没痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.53,0:01:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住 一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是打零工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要走上现实社会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有超乎想象的惊喜在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我叫来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为估计人很少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的大换血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 未经许可不要擅自行动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚本来打算好好享受宁静的暑假结尾的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个活动本来是宿舍代代相传
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有住宿生参加的传统…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏打放这里可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火热的夏天还没结束呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:39.99,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(594,326)\be1}（现在正在举行“真心话”烟花大会）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 其实期末考试时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里响起的奇怪雷声是我的肚子在叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮（注：原文玉屋，放烟花时表示赞赏）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 其实之前给拓人君做便当的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对着刚炸好的炸土豆饼花了5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注入lovelove念力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我经常让女仆帮我冲背
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我初吻的对象是我养的猫雷奥纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我不能吃青椒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哑炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 红绪穿泳装翻单杠100次是我偷拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃呃 那个…以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不对不对 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是拓人君输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子和袜子都脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是没什么可…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小煌 好像很好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点脱啊 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们似乎在做很有趣的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看板郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是脱衣舞？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这位似乎也很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然跑出来还真厚脸皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.24,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(530,322)\be1}（很危险 玩烟花的人千万不要模仿）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲哉 给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 快住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天真火热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热过头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好没人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是小火灾就了事已经算万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津名志同学的房间被烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后要考虑一下住宿才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可以寄宿在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢了须方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都烧完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假最后的活动就是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把换洗衣服放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了呢 累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 要我帮您冲背吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 总之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好把这个放口袋里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的表？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服和课本总有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的事明天再想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我也没怎么消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 毕竟是拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是须方君以前用过的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是须方小时候画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那涂鸦是我画的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候经常来这里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 给你看样好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君的相册
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候经常扮偶像玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 班长丹治惠都？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候经常一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 和子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人一起转进我们班了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富煌和慧窗华
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们班很有人气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给学长做了便当
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说是奖励做菜的手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那是奖励吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男朋友的暑假结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男朋友的新学期就开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子选定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿舍的火灾 够呛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩了下火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身家当都化成灰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话真是陷入绝境了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又得找打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在住哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且赖在须方家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我家也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩火怎么不跟我玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好像会严重烧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我在须方家看到相册了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你以前跟和子扮偶像组合？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是陈年往事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那照片和现在的印象差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:11:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可和子现在还说要当歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:24.57,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}等待着朝霞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:28.04,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不安的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:30.38,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寻回的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:33.71,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即便是无心的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.13,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}秋色的风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.77,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用老成的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:43.26,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将逝去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:45.76,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}教给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:49.03,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}来来往往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:52.07,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思考烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:59.84,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那唯一的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:05.53,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寻找着 一触即破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:09.45,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}等待着结局 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:12.20,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}令人忧伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:15.17,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}逼近心底的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:18.30,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}破坏中开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:22.17,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}诞生的生命 即使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.96,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:29.73,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中却已接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:35.94,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧闭的眼眸 已彼此相系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:37.91,EDCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 现实社会上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有超乎想象的惊喜在等待啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给店里帮忙又在玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样每天跳得这么兴高采烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为自己是偶像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:13:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是从今天开始在我们家打工的津名志君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的话招来当女婿也行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heigent（窗）还在搁浅中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能复原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先导出你和当前奥利哈康波动周期顶点的计算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快也需要几天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且选择复原的素体需要总会的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为可以更轻松地复原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想玩多少次就能玩多少次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了第四阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就不需要这些复杂的机械界面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以凭驭星者的意志随意复原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的阶段复原可是有生命危险的哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说失败可能会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启程之日到来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这些家伙驾着素体跑出零时空间肆意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界真的会有危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也变成无聊人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能早点玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有玩具好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是拥有真正印记的驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使素体坏了应该也可以用第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那似乎也很有趣
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.34,0:14:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公演快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了水野 还得招收新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说这是柔软体操
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如当成宣传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们还有人气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要好的样子真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于昨天的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不会告诉任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是戏剧部的粉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的粉丝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是2班的转校生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富煌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慧窗华
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对戏剧部没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1班的班长 丹治惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她大概就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们玩个开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才最优先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有社团活动的日子就不要练剑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能一招打倒我就停止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一脸不满的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换房租不收你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成交
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点抛弃那种天真的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用木刀练习本身就很天真了 二位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好罢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了 房东
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 食客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heigent 第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种刀法…是拓人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这黑暗是窗之星的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来全都是我窗之星的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我会袭击你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要打到自己人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pinch吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的小把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就让它结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这黑暗中 你只能识别出自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别出自己就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你下手轻一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.76,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(564,426)\be1}（很危险 使用第一阶段的人千万不要模仿）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤须方 真不可小视
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 只不过是自己怕死才这么做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 真是毫不留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种性格为什么还会受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是也说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君其实很温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 倒是让我白吃白住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候我要是扮偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是很开心地夸奖我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:21:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 班长也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长现在也对须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让逆日死之巫女做的工作是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 并不是我让她去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作辛苦了 逆日死大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一阵子都没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今晚又陷入了沉眠之底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.47,0:22:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.48,0:23:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周日是和子的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要亲手做料理庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 当我们来到城里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团的魔掌却逐渐逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.69,0:24:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人的周日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的银河 已经在闪耀
